data.description: Huge Price Reduced...Motivated Seller!  Stunning Lake views from this Executive 4 bedroom, 4 bath heated saltwater pool home with spa in the resort community of Islandwalk!     The Carlisle floor plan built by Divosta is a favorite with 2 separate guest wings for privacy.     Beautiful front porch and Beveled glass entry leads to the formal Livingroom with a cozy electric fireplace and formal dining-room.     Chefs Kitchen boasts stainless appliances, New dishwasher,  New stove with air-fryer, Corian counters, glass backsplash and breakfast bar that opens to the great room with a wall of glass sliders overlooking the pool and lake is perfect for entertaining.     Gorgeous distressed Oak hardwood flooring, neutral tile and carpeting throughout the home is a lovely combination. Great room has designer built in entertainment center with glass shelves, extensive crown molding and Hunter Douglas window treatments. Primary bedroom has sliders to the pool, custom closets and 2 separate baths.      Solid poured concrete home is Hurricane proof with new $50,000 High Wind Impact windows and Shutters for energy efficiency and peace of mind. New Dual Zone York AC has a 10 -year transferable warranty, additionally a 1-year home warranty from American Home Shield is offered. Central Vacuum, extensive tropical landscaping with brick paver driveway and sidewalk around the home with underground lighting is bonus added feature.     Resort community of Islandwalk is guard gated, has a full time activites director, 2 recreational centers with salt water heated pools and spa, clubhouse, tennis, Pickle ball and fitness center with Yoga studio. Call today for your private showing.
